comment5.target=boolean\ isEmpty()
comment5.text=\r\n\ Checks\ whether\ this\ item\ list\ contains\ no\ elements.\r\n\r\n\ @return\ {@code\ true}\ when\ no\ items\ are\ stored\r\n
