comment6.text=\r\n\ Builds\ a\ multi-line\ string\ with\ each\ item's\ description,\r\n\ or\ a\ default\ notice\ when\ the\ list\ is\ empty.\r\n\r\n\ @return\ formatted\ item\ descriptions\r\n
